description: Capacity Building of the Municipal Wastes Management System in the Kyrgyz Republic

subproject.description: This project is targeted to assist Kyrgyz Republic to introduce sustainable development principles to waste management area and develop National Production and Consumption Waste Management Strategy, increase capabilities for private sector involvement into waste management system, implement pilot projects related to efficient waste management, increase public awareness level in the sphere of waste management.
